{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"d4432e16-cbe9-4ea6-bb1f-5d08f1df8f30","content":"Here's how to migrate from `VSTest@3` to Microsoft.Testing.Platform while keeping TRX reports and code coverage:\n\n### 1. Update your test project\n\nIn your `.csproj`, add:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n  <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### 2. Replace `VSTest@3` with `dotnet test`\n\n**Before:**\n```yaml\n- task: VSTest@3\n  inputs:\n    testAssemblyVer2: '**\\*Tests.dll'\n    resultsFolder: $(Agent.TempDirectory)\\TestResults\n    codeCoverageEnabled: true\n```\n\n**After:**\n```yaml\n- task: DotNetCoreCLI@2\n  inputs:\n    command: test\n    projects: '**/*Tests.csproj'\n    arguments: >-\n      --results-directory $(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults\n      --logger \"trx;LogFileName=results.trx\"\n      --collect \"Code Coverage\"\n```\n\n### 3. Publish results & coverage\n\n```yaml\n- task: PublishTestResults@2\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    testResultsFormat: VSTest\n    testResultsFiles: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.trx'\n\n- task: PublishCodeCoverageResults@2\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    summaryFileLocation: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.cobertura.xml'\n```\n\n### Key differences\n\n| | VSTest@3 | Microsoft.Testing.Platform |\n|---|---|---|\n| Runner | `vstest.console.exe` | Test exe via `dotnet test` |\n| TRX | Built-in | `--logger trx` |\n| Coverage | `codeCoverageEnabled` | `--collect \"Code Coverage\"` |\n| Results publish | Automatic | Separate `PublishTestResults@2` step |\n\nThe `condition: always()` on the publish steps ensures reports are uploaded even when tests fail.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"d5faec3d-f5f0-40c0-ac1b-af5622eb2338","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The workspace is empty - the user is asking a general knowledge question about migrating from VSTest@3 to Microsoft.Testing.Platform in Azure DevOps pipelines. Let me provide a concise, helpful answer.","outputTokens":564,"requestId":"4C27:66EEF:D51076:1096187:6A0129EA"},"id":"153dd535-4e68-46a6-b2d4-a56e5b807ef3","timestamp":"2026-05-11T00:59:36.056Z","parentId":"87db44cf-af84-4d56-aa4c-fcfbaf902890"}
